@host = http://localhost:5252

# Set @tenantId to a tenant that has matching routing rules configured.
@tenantId = <paste-tenant-id-here>

### Ingest an event — dispatched if a matching rule exists
POST {{host}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "eventType": "order.created",
  "payload": "{\"orderId\": \"ord-001\", \"amount\": 49.99}"
}

###

### Ingest an event with no matching rule — will be dead-lettered
POST {{host}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "{{tenantId}}",
  "eventType": "unrouted.event",
  "payload": "{\"note\": \"no routing rule for this event type\"}"
}

###

### Ingest with an unknown tenant — 404
POST {{host}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "eventType": "order.created",
  "payload": "{}"
}
